summary: An ordinance appropriating the sum of $11.30 out of the General Fund of the City of Seattle, in favor of Ed L. Terry, as City Treasurer, for the purpose of reimbursing said Treasurer on account of check given by Jas. Lawn & Co., payable at the Bank of California in payment of Light Account of a like sum on March 10, 1911, upon which payment was refused on account of insufficient funds.
